OL,3,CChief Constable apologises to family
OL,4,Cof first child to die in the Troubles
OL,6,FThe family of the first child to die
OL,7,Fin the Troubles is set to receive
OL,8,F"significant compensation" over his
OL,9,Fkilling by police in west Belfast, the
OL,10,FHigh Court heard today.
OL,12,FAn apology was also issued for their
OL,13,Fhurt and suffering since nine-year-old
OL,14,FPatrick Rooney was shot dead in his
OL,15,Fown home at the Divis Flats back in
OL,16,FAugust 1969.
