OL,6,FThe settlement was announced in a
OL,7,Flegal action taken by the boy's
OL,8,Felderly mother against the Police
OL,9,FService of Northern Ireland (PSNI) for
OL,10,Fthe unlawful death.
OL,12,FUrging the authorities to ensure no
OL,13,Ffurther delays in approving the
OL,14,Fundisclosed figure, Mr Justice Rooney
OL,15,Fsaid: "This is an extraordinarily sad
OL,16,Fcase."
