OL,3,CChief Constable apologises to family
OL,4,Cof first child to die in the Troubles
OL,6,FPatrick died after Royal Ulster
OL,7,FConstabulary (RUC) officers opened
OL,8,Ffire from vehicle-mounted machine guns
OL,9,Fto deal with disturbances at the
OL,10,Fbeginning of the conflict.
OL,12,FHe had taken shelter along with his
OL,13,Ffive siblings and their parents,
OL,14,FNeilly and Alice, in a bedroom at
OL,15,Ftheir home in a bid to stay safe from
OL,16,Fthe shooting outside.
OL,18,FUp to 200 high velocity rounds were
OL,19,Fdischarged, striking a number of
OL,20,Fproperties in the tower blocks.
