OL,6,FPatrick, the eldest of the six
OL,7,Fchildren, was shot through the head in
OL,8,Ffront of the rest of his family.
OL,10,FHis parents were unable to secure
OL,11,Fmedical assistance at the scene.
OL,13,FInstead, his father Neilly and other
OL,14,Fmembers of the public had to carry him
OL,15,Ffrom the immediate area to reach an
OL,16,Fambulance.
