OL,6,FFollowing the fatal shooting members
OL,7,Fof the RUC took steps to prevent an
OL,8,Fadequate or effective probe into the
OL,9,Fcircumstances, according to the
OL,10,Ffamily's lawyers.
OL,12,FIn 2021 a Police Ombudsman report
OL,13,Fidentified significant operational and
OL,14,Finvestigative failures during the
OL,15,Fkilling of Patrick and three others in
OL,16,FBelfast at that time.
