OL,6,FThe use of Browning machine guns
OL,7,Fmounted on RUC Shorland vehicles to
OL,8,Fdeal with civil unrest in the area was
OL,9,Fcriticised as fundamentally flawed,
OL,10,Fdisproportionate and dangerous.
OL,12,FHowever, no surviving ex-police
OL,13,Fofficer was prosecuted due to a lack
OL,14,Fof evidence.
OL,16,FOmbudsman investigators were unable to
OL,17,Fidentify which vehicle the shot which
OL,18,Fkilled Patrick was fired from.
