OL,4,Cof first child to die in the Troubles
OL,6,FHis 88-year-old mother Alice sued the
OL,7,FChief Constable over both the shooting
OL,8,Fand the failure to conduct an
OL,9,Feffective inquiry or discipline the
OL,10,Fofficers responsible.
OL,12,FDamages were sought for negligence,
OL,13,Fbreach of statutory duty, assault and
OL,14,Fbattery, conspiracy to commit an
OL,15,Funlawful act, and misfeasance in
OL,16,Fpublic office.
OL,18,FMrs Rooney was unable to accompany
OL,19,Fother family members to court today
OL,20,Fdue to ill-health.
