OL,6,FBut her barrister, Patrick Lyttle KC,
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the terms of a
OL,8,Fsettlement have been reached.
OL,10,F"This is a tragic case arising out of
OL,11,Fthe death of Patrick Rooney at the age
OL,12,Fof nine," counsel said.
OL,14,F"He was struck by a bullet discharged
OL,15,Ffrom a heavy duty Browning machine gun
OL,16,Fmounted on a (Shorland) vehicle, shot
OL,17,Fin his own home."
OL,19,FUnder the terms of the resolution an
OL,20,Fapology was read out in open court.
