OL,6,F"The trauma this must have resulted in
OL,7,F(for the family) is just
OL,8,Funimaginable," Mr Justice Rooney said.
OL,10,F"His mother is still alive and clearly
OL,11,Fwants full resolution for what
OL,12,Fhappened in the most tragic
OL,13,Fcircumstances as soon as possible.
OL,15,F"Now that counsel has sensibly
OL,16,Fresolved this matter after such a long
OL,17,Ftime there should be no further delay."
OL,19,FOutside court, the Rooney family
OL,20,Fdescribed it as a "bittersweet"
OL,21,Foutcome.
