OL,6,FIn an emotional recollection of the
OL,7,Fevents surrounding Patrick's death, he
OL,8,Fadded: "It was horrific that night, I
OL,9,Fwas eight years old and imagined (the
OL,10,Fpolice) kicking the door in to line us
OL,11,Fup and shoot us.
OL,13,F"We were frightened out of our lives,
OL,14,Fthey petrified us."
